    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8063-99c2-e610a2a5255a",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The proposed algorithm uses a local brute-force approach that is still scaleable as it is NP in group sizes, but P in student numbers. Multiple experiemnts with different numbers of students show decent performance and running times. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8063-99c2-e610a2a5255a",
